            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt; 会德丰地产 PARK PENINSULA 两大临海合资现楼项目 MIAMI QUAY 及 DOUBLE COAST成交越趋炽热,今日共录得6宗成交,共套现逾4489万港元。<br/><br/>MIAMI QUAY 至今累售233伙,套现近逾27亿港元;DOUBLE COAST 至今累售401伙,套现逾31.5亿港元。 (BC)<br/><br/>#MIAMI QUAY #DOUBLE COAST #会德丰地产 </span>\n</div>",
